query_philosophy_type
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_philosophy_type

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_philosophy_type -  This method returns the type of the philosophy.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string query_philosophy_type(string name)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name of the philosophy to get the type of
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the type of the philosophy
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/philosophies.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the type of the philosophy.  An example of the
return value from this is "faith".
.EP

